<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10134135>
    dc:description "Figs 49–53. Male and female postabdomen of Siphona (Aphantorhaphopsis) curta sp. nov. (paratypes, Myanmar, Kambaiti). 49 – epandrium, cerci and surstylus in lateral view; 50 – epandrium, cerci and surstylus in dorsal view (setae omitted on left side); 51 – hypandrium, pregonite, postgonite and phallus in lateral view; 52 – fifth abdominal sternite in ventral view (setae omitted on left side); 53 – female postabdomen in lateral view. Scale bars = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10134135/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

